title: Restarted,Repaired,Redownloaded...still nothing
body: Hi Riot, I can't launch the game, everytime I get at 33% it says there is an error, I repaired and redownloaded the game and it just wont launch, I need help please.

replies.body: Everything should be okay now.  There was a patching issue for some players that have since been resolved.  Let me know if you have any problems with it still!
